Taylor Swift

Can Taylor Swift make it from her concert to the Super Bowl?

library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
concert <- ymd_hm("2024-02-10 18:00")
concert <- force_tz(concert, tzone = "Asia/Tokyo")

concert_end <- concert + hours(5)
concert_end <- force_tz(concert_end, tzone = "Asia/Tokyo")
concert_end_LA <- with_tz(concert_end, tzone = "America/Los_Angeles")
#tokyo is 17 hours ahead


superbowl <- ymd_hm("2024-02-11 15:30")
superbowl <- force_tz(superbowl, tzone = "America/Los_Angeles") 

time_dif <- as.numeric(difftime(superbowl, concert_end_LA, units = "hours"))

print(concert)
[1] "2024-02-10 18:00:00 JST"
print(concert_end)
[1] "2024-02-10 23:00:00 JST"
print(concert_end_LA)
[1] "2024-02-10 06:00:00 PST"
print(superbowl)
[1] "2024-02-11 15:30:00 PST"
print(time_dif)
[1] 33.5
print(time_dif-12)
[1] 21.5

Taylor will be at her concert in Tokyo on Saturday from 6 to 11pm. When her concert ends it is 6:00am on Saturday in LA. If the Superbowl is on Sunday at 3:30pm, she will have 33.5 hours between the two events. If the flight is 12 hours, she will still have 21.5 hours, or almost a day, to recover.

```{r setup}
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
```


```{r}
concert <- ymd_hm("2024-02-10 18:00")
concert <- force_tz(concert, tzone = "Asia/Tokyo")

concert_end <- concert + hours(5)
concert_end <- force_tz(concert_end, tzone = "Asia/Tokyo")
concert_end_LA <- with_tz(concert_end, tzone = "America/Los_Angeles")
#tokyo is 17 hours ahead


superbowl <- ymd_hm("2024-02-11 15:30")
superbowl <- force_tz(superbowl, tzone = "America/Los_Angeles") 

time_dif <- as.numeric(difftime(superbowl, concert_end_LA, units = "hours"))

print(concert)

print(concert_end)

print(concert_end_LA)
print(superbowl)
print(time_dif)
print(time_dif-12)
```

Taylor will be at her concert in Tokyo on Saturday from 6 to 11pm. When her concert ends it is 6:00am on Saturday in LA. If the Superbowl is on Sunday at 3:30pm, she will have 33.5 hours between the two events. If the flight is 12 hours, she will still have 21.5 hours, or almost a day, to recover.
